## Limitations

The information gathered is based on available online resources and may not encompass all existing strategies and initiatives. The effectiveness of prevention strategies can vary significantly depending on regional and cultural contexts, which may not be fully captured in this report. Additionally, the dynamic nature of human trafficking requires continuous updates to prevention strategies, which may not be reflected in the current data.

